article.linkText: Davenport carries Cincinnati over Florida A&M 78-50
article.story: CINCINNATI -- — Jeremiah Davenport posted 16 points as Cincinnati easily beat Florida A&M 78-50 on Tuesday night. Mika Adams-Woods had 11 points for Cincinnati (8-3). Ody Oguama added eight rebounds. Mike Saunders Jr. had six assists. MJ Randolph had 22 points and seven rebounds for the Rattlers (2-7). DJ Jones added 11 points. Bryce Moragne had 11 rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
